### 17. UploadAvatar

POST {{HOST}}/FileData/UploadAvatar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar-test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./avatar-test.png>
--boundary--

### 18. UploadFile

POST {{HOST}}/FileData/UploadFile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="helloworld.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./helloworld.txt>
--boundary--

